<h2 class="mt-12 mb-4">Making the Right Choice</h2>

<p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">WordPress remains viable for certain use cases, particularly content-heavy sites with multiple contributors who need user-friendly editing interfaces. However, for businesses prioritising AI visibility and performance, purpose-built solutions offer significant advantages.</p>

<p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">The choice ultimately depends on your priorities. If maximum AI visibility, performance, and security matter more than editing convenience, AI-optimised websites represent the future of web development.</p>
